{"tid":1493426,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搞9警察仔女系列","createTime":"2019-08-21T08:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T08:50:12.000Z","uid":189799,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"39ad49683a9015eee9f5c9d35126f8d67ecb8ca5","tid":1493426,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"有人話搞9黑警啲仔女，有人話禍不及妻兒。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得應該參考外國做法。<br />\n黑警通常都會同自己啲仔女講，話自己係正義嘅，拉啲壞人，維護法紀等等。做仔女嘅，自細比人洗腦，自然會信佢果套。<br />\n<br />\n所以可以學校附近貼多啲<br />\n你話拉壞人＞我貼721警黑勾結<br />\n你話維護法紀＞我貼虐打呀伯<br />\n你話你好正義＞我貼你濫用武力嘅圖<br />\n<br />\n比佢地知道自己父母最真實嘅一面，係幾咁醜惡。<br />\n貼得多，加上同學嘅討論，佢地會開始懷疑，然後自己上網搵真相。"},{"pid":"e7ccdf03c031015ce2a52e93ab575fb9c808e9ee","tid":1493426,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb91112285b5e0b000f97e5cfae18fffaad6d200","tid":1493426,"uid":166273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:50:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">禍必及全家</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}